Class UCDWordList.UCDWordComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ari.ucd.UCDWordList.UCDWordComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    UCDWordList

    protected class UCDWordList.UCDWordComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<UCDWord>
    Class used to sort the UCD words in this UCDWordList.

    Here, words are sorted case INsensitively without namespace. Thus, two identical words with a different namespace can NOT be in the same UCDWordList. The idea is to avoid any ambiguity for the users reading UCDs.

    Version:
    1.0 (02/2017)
    Author:
